{"tid":1570361,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說\"香港人，加油\"，試著說\"香港人，反抗！\"","createTime":"2019-09-15T04:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T09:36:56.000Z","uid":38819,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"02434f47e8f255ee75a629619a0847a814120b51","tid":1570361,"uid":38819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"成日喺街都聽到人叫「加油」<br />\n呢個只係一個打氣說話，講完都無咩做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係換做動詞<strong>「反抗」</strong>就唔同喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻醒晨晒！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面對廢藍無底線攻擊，最緊要識<strong>「反抗」</strong><br />\n尤其係人夠多嗰陣，全部人一齊大嗌<br />\n<strong>「香港人，反抗！」<br />\n「香港人，反抗！」<br />\n「香港人，反抗！」</strong><br />\n之後一路衝埋去班廢藍嗰度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加咗油3個月喇！<br />\n反抗啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>「香港人，反抗！」<br />\n「香港人，反抗！」<br />\n「香港人，反抗！」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申: 試過好多次帶「反抗」，但大家都係叫返「加油」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"617c53b44ce5816232321c43218e310dbe5a2b4d","tid":1570361,"uid":38819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"push!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddee13042dd3c38aa43dafc17b7027a68e23a3a6","tid":1570361,"uid":193233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:57:03.000Z","msg":"推！繼續叫！叫下叫下就有人跟！"},{"pid":"a461afe8fe1e25ad32b7594462e05b6d52f8771b","tid":1570361,"uid":38819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"Push! <img src=\"/ass